(8, 1, 'Yohaig', 'georginabowler@gmail.com', 'http://www.yohaig.ng/category/nigerian-newspapers/daily-post/', '216.151.183.87', '2017-07-17 12:56:45', '2017-07-17 12:56:45', 'The Nigeria Soccer Federation (NFF) yesterday defended Tremendous Eagles coach, Gernot Rohrs desire to \r\nwork from Europe, saying the association is to assist the coach uncover and choose credible overseas-primarily \r\nbased gamers for the senior nationwide group.\r\n\r\n\r\nSome soccer followers have criticized the Franco-German supervisor for his desire \r\nfor international-primarily based gamers and \r\nhis continued keep in Europe when Tremendous Eagles matches are performed in Nigeria.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nRohr can also be accused of not serving to to develop the home league together with his huge expertise in African soccer in contrast to his counterpart in Cameroon, who screens happenings within the countrys native scene.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nAmong the criticism is that Rohrs keep in Europe scouting for gamers of Nigerian descent has yielded little outcome.\r\n\r\nIt has additionally been argued that funds utilized in camping the group in France earlier than the disastrous AFCON qualifier towards South Africa would have served the nation higher \r\nif the group skilled in Nigeria earlier than the sport.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nReacting to those allegations, Tremendous Eagles Media Officer, Toyin Ibitoye, \r\nmentioned Rohr had by no means shied away from contributing to the \r\nevent of Nigerian soccer. He defined that the Eagles boss has been spending extra time in Europe to allow him uncover and choose \r\ngamers that could be used to qualify the workforce for the \r\nmost important championships.\r\n\r\n\r\nIbitoye reasoned that it could be troublesome for Rohr to get the best gamers for the Eagles if the best steps weren''t taken, including that it was not honest for some individuals to accuse Rohr of not \r\nspecializing in the Nigerian league.\r\n\r\n\r\n"The challenge of Rohr solely utilizing overseas-based mostly gamers for the World Cup and Nations Cup qualifiers and neglecting gamers within the home league is being over flogged. The coach works primarily with the international-based mostly gamers they''re the perfect obtainable for now.\r\n\r\n\r\n"You can''t anticipate him to be in Nigeria when all of the gamers he \r\nwants are in Europe. Rohr determined to depart the nation after the South Africa recreation to give attention to \r\nthe World Cup tie towards Cameroon. He was in Russia to look at the final Confederation Cup group recreation between Germany and Cameroon.', 0, '0', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 6.1; WOW64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Maxthon/4.4.3.4000 Chrome/30.0.1599.101 Safari/537.36', '', 0, 0);
