-section=faq--></p>\n<dl>\n<dt>Installation Instructions</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>The automatic plugin installer should work for most people. Manual installation is easy and takes fewer than five minutes.</p>\n<ol>\n<li>Download the plugin, unpack it and upload the &#8216;DS Woocommerce Next Previous Category Products&#8217; folder to your wp-content/plugins directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress.</li>\n<li>Navigate to Settings =&gt; Next Previous products settings.</li>\n</ol>\n</dd>\n<dt>Navigations are not appearing</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>Tick Enable option under Settings =&gt; Next Previous products settings</p>\n</dd>\n<dt>I have enabled the plugin but still navigations are not appearing?</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>Navigation will appear on product detail page. The product should be assigned under any product category.</p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p><!--section=changelog--></p>\n<h4>1.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First version</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:82:"https://wordpress.org/plugins/ds-woocommerce-next-previous-category-products/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:39:"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:5:{s:0:"";a:6:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:26:"Simpler Syntax Highlighter";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:57:"https://wordpress.org/plugins/simpler-syntax-highlighte