SD, GBP, EUR</li>\n<li>Full control over look and feel, easy to customize</li>\n<li>Responsive Layout</li>\n<li>Live Preview while making changes</li>\n<li>No Page reload</li>\n<li>Shortcode [what-if-bitcoin] can be used anywhere in the website</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>Future Roadmap:</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>More Cryptocurrency options&#8230;</li>\n<li>Share Feature after getting the result</li>\n<li>More Currency added other than USD, GBP, EUR</li>\n<li>You can request the features <a href="https://techuptodate.com.au/what-if-bitcoin/" rel="nofollow">here</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Note: This plugin is using API from https://www.coindesk.com/api/</p>\n<p><!--section=installation--></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Install <code>what-if-bitcoin</code> via the plugin directory or Upload the entire <code>what-if-bitcoin</code> folder to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress.</li>\n<li>You will find &#8216;What If Bitcoin?&#8217; menu in your WordPress admin panel.</li>\n<li>Then set your required plugin setting </li>\n<li>Just copy paste this shortcode [what-if-bitcoin] to any page or in the widget.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>For basic usage, you can also have a look at the <a href="https://techuptodate.com.au/what-if-bitcoin/" rel="nofollow">plugin web site</a>.</p>\n<p><!--section=faq--></p>\n<dl>\n<dt>Installation Instructions</dt>\n<dd>\n<ol>\n<li>Install <code>what-if-bitcoin</code> via the plugin directory or Upload the entire <code>what-if-bitcoin</code> folder to the <code>/wp-content/plugins/</code> directory.</li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress.</li>\n<li>You will find &#8216;What If Bitcoin?&#8217; menu in your WordPress admin panel.</li>\n<li>Then set your required plugin setting </li>\n<li>Just copy paste this shortcode [what-if-bitcoin] to any page or in the widget.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>For basic usage, you can also have a look at the <a href="https://techuptodate.com.au/what-if-bitcoin/" rel="nofollow">plugin web site</a>.</p>\n</dd>\n<dt>Do you have questions or issues with the plugin?</dt>\n<dd>\n<p>Use these support channels appropriately or Contact us <a href="https://techuptodate.com.au/what-if-bitcoin/" rel="nofollow">here</a></p>\n</dd>\n</dl>\n<p><!--section=changelog--></p>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial release.</li>\n</ul>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:51:"https://wordpress.org/plugins/what-if-bitcoin/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:3:{s:4:"href";s:46:"https://wordpress.org/plugins/browse/new/feed/";s:3:"rel";s:4:"self";s:4:"type";s:19:"application/rss+xml";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:44:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/syndication/";a:2:{s:12:"updatePeriod";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"\n	hourly	";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:15:"updateFrequency";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:4:"\n	1	";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}}}}}}s:4:"type";i:128;s:7:"headers";a:10:{s:6:"server";s:5:"nginx";s:4:"date";s:29:"Mon, 22 Jan 2018 18:48:05 GMT";s:12:"content-type";s:34:"application/rss+xml; charset=UTF-8";s:10:"connection";s:5:"close";s:25:"strict-transport-security";s:11:"max-age=360";s:6:"x-olaf";s:3:"";s:13:"last-modified";s:29:"Mon, 22 Jan 2018 18:31:17 GMT";s:4:"link";s:66:"<https://wordpress.org/plugins/wp-json